      "id": "69ef78a467ea12a03c183358",
      "text": "ページ作業メモ(井戸端メンテ部 2026/04/27)",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301669,
      "updated": 1777301669
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef78a40000000000e7abb3",
      "text": " [井戸端メンテ部]のページで説明に使う画像を差し替えた",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301669,
      "updated": 1777301759
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef79030000000000e7abbf",
      "text": " その時の画像を探すやり取りをページから取り除いてこちらに残しとく",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301764,
      "updated": 1777301812
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef78a40000000000e7abb4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301669,
      "updated": 1777301730
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef78a40000000000e7abb5",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/1d09b726167de9452798dcf37359e39a]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301669,
      "updated": 1777301669
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef78a40000000000e7abb6",
      "text": " この画像を差し替えたい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301669,
      "updated": 1777301669
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef78a40000000000e7abb7",
      "text": "  案内を置いたページのスクショに☓を入れたものでなく、案内を置いてない略称のページの画像を使いたい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301669,
      "updated": 1777301966
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef78a40000000000e7abb8",
      "text": "  そんなちょうどいいページを見つけられるだろか……[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301669,
      "updated": 1777301669
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef78a40000000000e7abb9",
      "text": "  [レヴィ=ストロース]とか？[who18.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301669,
      "updated": 1777301819
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef78a40000000000e7abba",
      "text": "  ありがとう！！！[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301669,
      "updated": 1777301817
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef79440000000000e7abc2",
      "text": "   フルネームに対する省略名で、なおかつ空リンクで、他のページからリンクされてるものなんて探せそうになかったから助かった！！",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301829,
      "updated": 1777301971
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef78eb0000000000e7abbb",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/bc0734e2aba3a14700c85c2f113d2bc3]]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301740,
      "updated": 1777301823
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef79400000000000e7abc1",
      "text": "   良くなった",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777301824,
      "updated": 1777301825
    },
    {
      "id": "69ef7b86000000000009df88",
      "text": "   [/icons/わいわい.icon] [who18.icon]",
